{
  "id": "adv_card_kan_05_01",
  "title": "kana 1話 セレブという名の獲物",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "speakerNameEn": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――ライブ前日",
      "translations": {
        "en": "――The Day Before the Live",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 0,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_mall-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "mall-00-noon",
      "startTime": 1.2
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "speakerNameEn": "kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_05_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_05_01-kan001.m4a",
      "text": "ふーん、ここがラスベガスのショッピングモールか……\n確かにいろいろでかい気はするけど、結構普通かも",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Hmm‚ so this is a shopping mall in Las Vegas…\nIt’s true that everything’s huge‚ but it’s kinda normal.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 7.7,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-in-single-02.m4a",
          "delay": 0,
          "startTime": 1.8333333333
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_mall-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "mall-00-noon",
      "startTime": 12.566666619
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "speakerNameEn": "kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_05_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_05_01-kan002.m4a",
      "text": "その辺歩いてる奴らもカジュアルな感じだし\nラスベガスでも、みんなギラギラって訳でもないのか",
      "translations": {
        "en": "The people walking around are pretty casual too‚\nand not everyone in Vegas is all glitzy and glamorous.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 16.4333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_mall-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "mall-00-noon",
      "startTime": 20.566666619
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "speakerNameEn": "kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_05_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_05_01-kan003.m4a",
      "text": "っていうか、腰が引けた歩き方いい加減止めろっての\nあんた、アメリカ来たことないの？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "And hey‚ stop walking like you’re scared.\nIs this your first time in America?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 25.3666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_05_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_05_01-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "仕事で海外に来たのは、今回が初めてでして",
      "translations": {
        "en": "This is my first time working overseas…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 27.9999999523,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_mall-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "mall-00-noon",
      "startTime": 32.9999999523
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "speakerNameEn": "kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_05_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_05_01-kan004.m4a",
      "text": "ふーん。ならなおさら、kanaに感謝しなさいよ\nkanaが英語出来るおかげで、通訳もいらないし",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Hmm. Then you should be even more grateful to me.\nThanks to kana’s English skills‚ we don’t even need an interpreter.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 38.1666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_mall-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "mall-00-noon",
      "startTime": 42.0999999523
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "speakerNameEn": "kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_05_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_05_01-kan005.m4a",
      "text": "そもそもkanaの動画がバズったおかげで\nあんたも経費でラスベガスまで来れたんだから",
      "translations": {
        "en": "In the first place‚ you’re here in Las Vegas\non an expense account because my videos went viral.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 45.3666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_mall-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "mall-00-noon",
      "startTime": 48.9999999523
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_05_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_05_01-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "そ、そうですね\nそれでkanaさん。このショッピングモールで\nセレブっぽく豪遊するって話でしたけど……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "T-that’s true.\nSo‚ kana-san‚ you were saying something about\nflaunting your wealth like celebrities at this shopping mall…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 54.3333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "speakerNameEn": "kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_05_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_05_01-kan006.m4a",
      "text": "そうそう。日本からトップアイドルがラスベガスに\n来てるって、観光客に噂してもらいたいからね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yeah‚ yeah. I want the tourists to spread the rumor\nthat a top idol from Japan is in Las Vegas.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 61.8333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_mall-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "mall-00-noon",
      "startTime": 65.9333332856
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "speakerNameEn": "kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_05_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_05_01-kan007.m4a",
      "text": "そんでもって、kana達のライブも満員御礼\n大成功させてみせるんだから",
      "translations": {
        "en": "And then‚ I’m gonna make kana’s live\na huge sold-out success!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 69.7333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_mall-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "mall-00-noon",
      "startTime": 72.3999999523
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "speakerNameEn": "kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_05_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_05_01-kan008.m4a",
      "text": "まー、もうちょい駄目押ししたいとこではあるんだけど\nそっちはうまいこと獲物が見つかるか分かんないしなぁ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Well‚ I wouldn’t mind pushing it a little further…\nBut I don’t know if I’ll find good prey.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 76.9666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_05_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_05_01-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "……獲物？　一体何をするつもりなんですか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…Prey? What are you planning to do?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 81.6333332856,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_mall-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "mall-00-noon",
      "startTime": 85.966666619
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "speakerNameEn": "kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_05_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_05_01-kan009.m4a",
      "text": "んー、あの辺りの店から行ってみるか",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Hmm‚ let’s try that store over there.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 85.966666619,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_05_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_05_01-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "ちょっと待って下さい\nあそこ、俺でも分かるくらいの高級ブランドですよ？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Hold on a second!\nThat’s a super high-end brand‚ even I know that!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 92.2524342958,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_mall-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "mall-00-noon",
      "startTime": 96.2333332856
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "speakerNameEn": "kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_05_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_05_01-kan010.m4a",
      "text": "だから行くんでしょうが。「日本から大物が来てる！」\nって噂してもらいたいんだから",
      "translations": {
        "en": "That’s why I’m going! I want people to spread the rumor\nthat a big shot from Japan is here!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 100.5333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_mall-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "mall-00-noon",
      "startTime": 102.866666619
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_05_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_05_01-koh005.m4a",
      "text": "それは分かりますけど、franさんみたいに\nkanaさんにまで金金言われると、俺の胃が……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I understand that‚ but… Hearing you talk about money\nlike fran-san does… makes me feel sick…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 106.0198160721,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "speakerNameEn": "kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_05_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_05_01-kan011.m4a",
      "text": "kanaは金持ってんの\nBIG4だった頃は凄い稼いでたんだから",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I have money‚ you know.\nI made a ton of money when I was in BIG4.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 113.5333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "speakerNameEn": "kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_05_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_05_01-kan012.m4a",
      "text": "あと、あの銭ゲバと一緒にしないでもらえる！？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "And don’t lump me in with that money-grubber!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 116.966666619,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_mall-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "mall-00-noon",
      "startTime": 116.966666619
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_apparelshop-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "apparelshop-00-noon",
      "startTime": 121.8833332856
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_apparelshop-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "apparelshop-00-noon",
      "startTime": 121.8833332856
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_05_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_05_01-koh006.m4a",
      "text": "（店内の重厚感が、もう普通の店とはまるで違うな……）\n（しかし、kanaさんは平然としている……）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（The atmosphere in this store is so heavy… It’s completely different from a regular store…）\n（But kana-san is completely unfazed…）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 128.3666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_apparelshop-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "apparelshop-00-noon",
      "startTime": 131.8333332856
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "speakerNameEn": "kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_05_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_05_01-kan013.m4a",
      "text": "『ねえ。ここの棚のバッグ\nこれとこれとこれ、色違いで全部ちょうだい』",
      "translations": {
        "en": "“Excuse me. Those bags on the shelf right there…\nI’ll take this one‚ this one‚ and this one‚ in every color.”",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 134.4666666667,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_zawa-02.m4a",
          "delay": 6566.666714400015,
          "startTime": 138.4
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_apparelshop-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "apparelshop-00-noon",
      "startTime": 139.3999989351
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "speakerNameEn": "kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_05_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_05_01-kan014.m4a",
      "text": "ふふん、驚いてる驚いてる\nあ～もう、ラスベガス来てからこの反応に飢えてたのよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Fufun‚ they’re surprised‚ surprised.\nAhhh~ I’ve been craving this reaction ever since we got to Vegas.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 143.2999989828,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "speakerNameEn": "kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_05_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_05_01-kan015.m4a",
      "text": "みんなkanaのこと、大スターだと思ってるみたい\nま、スターなのは本当のことだけど！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Everyone seems to think I’m a superstar.\nWell‚ it’s true that I’m a star!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 152.4989038317,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_apparelshop-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "apparelshop-00-noon",
      "startTime": 155.7999989351
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "speakerNameEn": "kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_05_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_05_01-kan016.m4a",
      "text": "んじゃ。はい、{user}\nほら、ぼさっとしてないで荷物を持つ！！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Alright‚ here‚ {user}.\nDon’t just stand there‚ carry the bags!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 159.1333323162,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_down-01.m4a",
          "delay": 6166.66671439998,
          "startTime": 161.9666656495
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_apparelshop-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "apparelshop-00-noon",
      "startTime": 164.8999999524
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "speakerNameEn": "kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_05_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_05_01-kan017.m4a",
      "text": "お！　このバッグ、日本未発売の限定色じゃん！\nやー、こういうのを探してたのよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Oh! This bag is a limited edition color that’s not available in Japan!\nI’ve been looking for something like this.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 170.3999989828,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
